Project Setup Rules:

- DO NOT access or read from `.env.local`
- Instead, output full echo commands (one per line) so I can paste them manually
- Default to Windows/PowerShell syntax for CLI commands
- Assume no Linux tools (no `touch`, `export`, `cat`, etc.)
